---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us">
  <Header />

  <main class="py-8">
    <HeroSection 
      title="About Us" 
      description="Choose a plan that fits your mission. All options include a 14-day free trial—no credit card required."
    />

    ---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-secondary-900 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About Green Orbit Digital</h1>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Accelerating Sustainable Growth in the Space Sector</h2>
    <p>We exist to empower space organisations to thrive — responsibly, transparently, and sustainably.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Priorities</h2>
    <p>We help forward-looking space companies grow through strategic, data-driven, and sustainability-focused marketing. Our work enables organisations to better communicate their impact, navigate emerging challenges, and align their growth with global sustainability goals.</p>
    <p>As an independent agency, our purpose is not to drive shareholder returns, but to create lasting impact — for our clients, their stakeholders, and the planet. We invest in knowledge-sharing, industry advocacy, and best practice to advance sustainable progress in the space ecosystem.</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-4 space-y-1">
      <li>🌍 Championing sustainability as a driver of commercial growth</li>
      <li>📡 Supporting organisations to build digital trust in the space economy</li>
      <li>🔬 Bringing clarity to complex scientific, technical, and policy narratives</li>
      <li>🤝 Partnering with startups, scale-ups, and space leaders to deliver long-term impact</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-4">
      <a href="/services" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline mr-4">Explore Our Services</a> | 
      <a href="/capabilities" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Discover Our Capabilities</a>
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Purpose</h2>
    <p><strong>Impact-Driven Marketing for a Sustainable Space Economy</strong></p>
    <p>Our mission is to help space organisations grow their reach, reputation, and revenue through marketing that aligns with planetary boundaries.</p>
    <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-green-600 pl-4 italic my-4">
      “We exist to make sustainable space marketing the norm — not the niche. That’s how we help our clients grow, build trust, and shape a better future.”
    </blockquote>
    <p>From reducing the footprint of digital campaigns to amplifying sustainable innovation, everything we do is rooted in driving positive outcomes — commercially, environmentally, and socially.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Who We Are</h2>
    <p>Founded by Chartered Marketer Ryan Laird, Green Orbit Digital brings together deep industry experience in the space sector with cutting-edge marketing expertise.</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-4 space-y-1">
      <li>🎙 Hosts of The Sustainable Space Podcast</li>
      <li>🎓 Chair of the UKspace Startup Working Group</li>
      <li>🛰 Trusted by space-tech startups, primes, and ecosystem enablers</li>
      <li>🇬🇧 Based in the UK, working with clients globally</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-4">We are proud to work at the intersection of space, sustainability, and strategy.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our History</h2>
    <p>A Future-First Agency with Deep Roots in the Space Industry</p>
    <p>With over a decade in space marketing, Green Orbit Digital was launched to meet a growing demand: marketing that makes sense in a climate-conscious world.</p>
    <p>Since then, we’ve helped space organisations:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-4 space-y-1">
      <li>Launch sustainable brands</li>
      <li>Enter new markets</li>
      <li>Communicate their impact with authority and clarity</li>
      <li>Align their growth with environmental and societal goals</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-4"><a href="/insights" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Explore Insights & Media</a></p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Sustainability</h2>
    <p><strong>Sustainability Is Not Just What We Say — It’s How We Work</strong></p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-4 space-y-1">
      <li>Digital-first, low-impact marketing execution</li>
      <li>Partnerships with environmentally responsible platforms</li>
      <li>Measurement frameworks aligned with ESG and SDGs</li>
      <li>Guidance on reducing the footprint of your marketing channels</li>
      <li>Continuous learning through sustainability reporting and improvement</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-4"><a href="/sustainability" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Explore our Sustainable Marketing Practices</a></p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Why Green Orbit Digital?</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-4 space-y-1">
      <li>✅ We bring specialist marketing expertise and space industry fluency</li>
      <li>✅ We’re values-driven, not volume-driven</li>
      <li>✅ We focus on outcomes, not just outputs</li>
      <li>✅ We measure both growth and impact</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-4">Our model ensures that your success — whether commercial or reputational — is always aligned with broader planetary benefit.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Community</h2>
    <p>We are proud to collaborate with a global network of:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-4 space-y-1">
      <li>🌍 Sustainable space startups</li>
      <li>🏛 Government and policy stakeholders</li>
      <li>📢 Marketing innovators and communications experts</li>
      <li>🚀 Academics, scientists, and researchers shaping the space future</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-4"><a href="/clients" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Meet Our Clients & Collaborators</a></p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Governance & Ethics</h2>
    <p>As a purpose-led agency, we commit to the highest standards of transparency, inclusivity, and ethical conduct.</p>
    <p>Our work is guided by a simple principle:<br /><em>Marketing must be honest, inclusive, and net-positive.</em></p>
    <p>We regularly assess our own practices, align with sector-wide standards (such as the UN SDGs and ISO 14001), and advocate for ethical marketing practices across the space ecosystem.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Values</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-4 space-y-1">
      <li><strong>Purpose-Led</strong> — We partner with clients who share our commitment to impact. We’re relentless in using marketing to make a better world possible.</li>
      <li><strong>Partnership-First</strong> — We co-create with clients, listening first and acting with integrity. Their success is our success.</li>
      <li><strong>Progress-Oriented</strong> — We don’t stand still. We evolve, experiment, and challenge norms to drive progress.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Careers</h2>
    <p>Join Us in Shaping the Sustainable Space Economy</p>
    <p>Are you a marketer, strategist, or creative who believes in purpose over profit?<br />
    Come work with us and use your skills to make a measurable difference.</p>
    <p class="mt-4"><a href="/careers" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Explore Careers</a></p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
    <p>Let’s build your brand for a better space future.<br />
    Whether you’re launching, scaling, or redefining your mission, we can help.</p>
    <p class="mt-4"><a href="/contact" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Get in Touch</a></p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Explore More</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
      <li><a href="/services" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Our Services</a></li>
      <li><a href="/capabilities" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Our Capabilities</a></li>
      <li><a href="/podcast" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Our Podcast</a></li>
      <li><a href="/insights" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Insights & Media</a></li>
      <li><a href="/careers" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Work With Us</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout> 
